{
  "texts": [
    "For evaluation, we first hand-labeled a dataset of Appendix D shows the system and the user prompts that were used for the ChatGPT-3.5 Turbo model.",
    "In almost all cases, the ChatGPT model returned just the category name.",
    "However, in 3-5 instances per model, the ChatGPT model ran into an error and returned no category name.",
    "Those responses were classified by hand.",
    "Given that aggressive pruning reduces an LLM's overall abilities (Sun et al., 2023), it is important to benchmark the pruned models across various tasks to ensure they remain capable."
  ]
}